Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:04.71,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Dammit! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.44,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,I can't produce my fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.69,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Marlefiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.07,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Hurry up and heal me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.62,Default,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,I already am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:16.22,Default,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,But I'm not putting out my usual power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:21.33,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Hey, newbie! Can't you use fire magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.33,Default,Mage,0,0,0,,You said you could use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:25.47,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Tsk! Useless idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:26.52,Default,MAge,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.39,Default,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:29.71,DefaultTop,Marlefiss,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.15,DefaultItalics,Bandana,0,0,0,,This party is already done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:07.31,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,They want me as the director of a \Nroyal magic technology research lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.88,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,They'll treat me like a noble?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:09.85,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:12.82,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,How did something that incredible happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:15.50,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,The person I had appraise your magic crystals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.03,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,serves as a royal court mage as a hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.24,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Are you sure she's not deceiving you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:25.38,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Well, I know it's hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:26.35,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,but what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.94,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.33,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,It certainly is a good offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.67,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,but please turn it down for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.88,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.81,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I can't imagine myself working in \Na role that puts me above others,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:43.29,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,and part of me still wants to go back\Nto Flaming Dragon Fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.67,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:47.89,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,My current job is working here after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.40,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Kurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:56.36,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,The magic crystals you went and sold \Nweren't enough to pay your taxes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:03:00.82,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I sold them for quite a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.92,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,but I didn't make those myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:10.21,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I just took one gold as a handler's fee \Nand deposited the rest into your account.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.37,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,You didn't need to worry about me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.92,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.20,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,If I accepted such a hefty sum,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.38,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I would be crushed under the guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.30,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.84,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.55,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,But that's why I'd like you \Nto keep digging up ore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.40,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:31.68,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I found what looks like it might \Nbe a good vein yesterday too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.98,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You're a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.31,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,But Kurt, you haven't slept, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.28,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I got six hours of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.07,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Six hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.32,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.66,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Even though you built that log house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.91,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Five hours to fell the trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:47.66,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,three hours to process them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.04,DefaultTop,Yulishia,0,0,0,,four hours to put it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.04,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I sleep too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:53.17,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Back when I was with Flaming Dragon \NFang I only got around four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.60,DefaultTop,Yulishia,0,0,0,,That leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.59,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,They said the one in charge of \Nchores had to wake up earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.05,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,and go to sleep later than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.88,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Umm, I promise to make up for how much I rested!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:03.85,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.42,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,This is where you think you found a good spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.21,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.17,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I don't see anything out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.48,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.27,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Though considering the \Ntopography of the mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.59,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,there should be an ore deposit beneath here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:21.25,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,But please don't dig \Nany deeper than 50 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.20,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,50?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.20,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be heading elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.91,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You won't be digging with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:31.12,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,No. I plan to dig around the area where \Nwe found that large crystal yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.80,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,All right. I'll leave that to you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.50,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll be heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.93,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.79,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,This is a topaz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.48,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's rather big!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.96,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I bet this would go for around three gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.64,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I bet I could ask Kurt to turn it \Ninto a magic crystal for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.71,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Then I'd have plenty to reach my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.52,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:02.36,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be trying to use \Nthat innocent boy for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.71,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I wonder what Kurt is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:09.89,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Knowing him, he's probably \Nmade a whole mining tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.37,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I expect that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.96,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,but see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.45,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.50,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,We don't need lamps due to luminous moss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.84,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Well, that's within expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.02,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Even so, this space is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:32.04,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's three times bigger than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.60,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,But this is Kurt we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.68,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,So that's within expectations too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:37.64,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, Yulishia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:40.52,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I was just thinking of heading over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.32,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to ask, but how'd it turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.89,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.97,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,All I've mined have been useless rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:53.04,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,and I've only mined tiny \Nfragments of the ore I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.68,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I see, I see. That's goo—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.11,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.45,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Are those the useless rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.46,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.64,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,They look like rather pretty stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.19,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm able to mine a lot of them though, \Nso they're not very valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.05,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,They're called mythril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.89,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Mythril?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.42,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,You know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.35,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,We harvest so much of it in my \Nvillage that we threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.26,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Do I know about it?! That's a far more \Nvaluable ore than gold or even platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.07,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,And he throws it away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.03,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:33.45,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Are you saying that it's valuable around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.74,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Is it hard to acquire in the city or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:39.82,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's an extremely rare ore throughout \Nthe world. And yet he...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:43.67,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Wait. Then what is the ore you \Nsaid you were after earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.26,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.15,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Orichalcum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.38,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,The legendary ore known \Nas the metal of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.18,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I can't believe there's something \Nlike that in this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.52,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh? You can generally mine it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.27,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,There's no way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:01.00,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,You can often find it after digging \Nabout 7km into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.02,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,7km?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:06.53,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You dug down 7km in 8 hours and came \Nall the way back up to the surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.73,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.86,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Well, this is you we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.80,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,By the way, what about the shaft?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.87,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,It would be dangerous to \Nleave it, so I filled it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.92,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You even refilled it within 8 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.77,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to surprise me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.22,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.56,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You dug right through the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.02,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,This new tunnel looks convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.59,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Should I fill it back in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.84,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,You don't need to fill it.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.94,0:07:53.24,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I finished the mining in two \Ndays and we returned to Samaela.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.24,0:07:57.71,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,That tunnel was positioned to connect the \Ncity of Samaela to Lord Taicone's town.
