Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:04.37,scrolls,MapTop,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1)\move(239,12,239,102)}Frontier Town
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.71,0:08:01.15,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Apparently Yulishia agreed to permit \Nthose with the traveling merchants guild
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.17,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,to pass through it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.37,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,in return for them paying\N a maintenance fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.34,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,She told me the profit from \Nthat would cover her taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.34,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Kur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.22,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, Bandana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.76,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.33,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.19,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Is Golnova with you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:21.35,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh, I ain't a part of Flaming \NDragon Fang anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:21.73,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.19,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,A bunch of stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.77,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,I can't eat trash like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.99,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Sir, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.15,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.59,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Ah, Sir, your bill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.31,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Obviously I ain't paying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.97,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,S-Sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.77,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Somebody! Please call the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.54,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,How was eating at that popular restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:50.25,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,I worked hard to get them \Nto squeeze in a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.76,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Bandana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.72,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,We still have that smoked meat \NKur made before he left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.37,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,It's all gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.99,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,You ate it all, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.94,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Then go fetch Kur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.77,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Make him cook food for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:06.41,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,If he fights back, then I don't \Ncare if you have to hurt him a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.21,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Sure thing. You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.72,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:15.51,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll need to borrow \Nthe teleportation crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:17.61,Default,Golnova,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.45,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,The culprit fled into this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.83,Default,Captain,0,0,0,,Be alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.53,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:26.68,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Guess he would get arrested \Nafter making such a commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.71,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Marlefiss lucked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.46,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,being summoned away by the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.84,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Now Flaming Dragon Fang is truly finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.62,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Well, I'll pay you a visit in \Nprison if I feel like it, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:46.02,DefaultItalics,Bandana,0,0,0,,I'll leave out all of that and \Nsay I was simply fired too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.73,DefaultItalics,Bandana,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want my surveillance \Ntarget involved in that mess too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.69,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I can't believe you were fired too, Bandana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:59.11,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,It's definitely impossible for me to \Nreturn to Flaming Dragon Fang then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:02.12,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Why are you so set on that party anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:08.08,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Because I owe Golnova a lot, and I admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.96,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Admire him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:14.86,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,He certainly did serve as an excellent front.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.80,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Kur, if you're going to Hallo Work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.93,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,then that means you're looking for work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:22.76,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:24.18,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:28.73,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,I actually have an acquaintance who's short \Non hands and struggling in their workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.56,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Could you go give them a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.06,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,A workshop, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:37.24,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,There are only 15 Atelier Meisters with \Nofficial permission from the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.94,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,One of those incredible \Npeople is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:44.08,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,If you'd go to them, it would be a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.91,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,You think I'd be useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.38,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Have more confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.93,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,I'm recommending you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:53.82,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,All right, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.92,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Then here's a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.26,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.39,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.02,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'll head out, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:10.32,Default,Bandana,0,0,0,,Good grief. Being the Great Sage's \Napprentice isn't an easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.90,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,The workshops known as Ateliers are facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:19.84,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,that primarily produce and sell medicines, \Nmagic swords, magic devices and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:25.33,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,The head of an Atelier with official \Npermission is known as an Atelier Meister,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.04,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,and they're granted special rights with \Nregards to development and distribution,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.21,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,along with being treated as \Nequal to a Viscount in standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:36.63,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I never knew there was an \Nofficial Atelier in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:40.81,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,But is this really the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:44.51,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,It looks like a normal person's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.30,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,This is definitely it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:55.15,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,W-Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:58.36,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Is such a young girl the Atelier Meister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:01.82,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,Umm, are you unfamiliar with elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.32,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.46,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm sorry, that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.55,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,My name is Kurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.83,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Are you the Atelier Meister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:18.30,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,No, I'm the Atelier Meister's \Nassistant, Michelle Lalacotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.96,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I came here to help on Bandana's recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.86,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,Ah! Someone's actually come to help us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.04,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.06,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,P-Please come inside for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.06,DefaultTop,Kurt,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.94,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:41.10,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,Uhh, I'd like to ask you \Nto help clean up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:44.40,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to get to \Nit for three whole weeks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.58,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:50.19,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I've been called in to help with housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.96,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I guess it was too much to hope\Nthey'd let me work in the atelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.16,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:58.67,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm bad at cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:13:00.04,DefaultTop,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Michelle! Come help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.91,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,Yes! Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.57,Default,Michelle,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. My master is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.44,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.62,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.15,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Time to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.19,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,That took a whole 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.34,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I wonder what I should do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.41,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,If I recall, Michelle went this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.79,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Yes, come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.32,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.77,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Umm, where's Michelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:45.96,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:48.75,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.32,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Umm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.53,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,and you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.99,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,U-Uhh, my name's Kurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.52,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I started working here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.64,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.43,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Lady Ophelia has gone down into the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.01,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.58,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:11.98,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.01,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,That mark on your stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:17.15,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.46,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.08,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,It's a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.63,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.29,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,May I take a closer look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:25.80,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.51,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,May I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.81,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.23,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Looks like there's no pain when I touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:37.73,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,More specifically, the curse has eaten away \Nat her so much she can't feel any pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.40,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I imagine her organs are rather damaged as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.19,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,That would make eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.93,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Oh. I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.06,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:49.86,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,She still has a proper appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.83,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'll prepare something \Nlight for you to eat, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.56,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I just now realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:01.79,DefaultItalics,Kurt,0,0,0,,I was touching a naked woman's body quite a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:06.25,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,God, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.20,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.09,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,How much is it worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.35,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,50,000 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.64,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,That's outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.46,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,It is outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.01,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Both mythril and orichalcum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.44,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,I can't believe they're real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:29.94,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Mimico, what do you think would \Nhappen if word got out about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.28,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,If he's lucky, he'd be kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.98,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Worst case, assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:39.87,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,How has such a monstrous young boy \Nmanaged to remain hidden all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.08,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I heard he was fired from Flaming Dragon Fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.08,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Flaming Dragon Fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:48.25,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,I heard their leader's a wanted man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:48.69,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.80,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,So what are you planning \Nto do with that boy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:55.10,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,I'm hoping to get him set \Nup as an Atelier Meister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.28,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Having his actions limited to some degree
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.77,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,would be much better than him \Nstanding out all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:03.21,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Then I plan to have him \Nemploy me as a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:04.23,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Mhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.52,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,The real question is how \Nto get him to accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.78,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,He has no awareness of his real capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.73,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Worse, he undervalues himself far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.92,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,It's definitely going to be a struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.86,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Umm, are you Lady Ophelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.37,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.38,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I used your kitchen \Nwithout asking your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.73,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.73,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Porridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.27,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:44.23,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,The girl in the room in back \Nsaid she was feeling hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.64,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,You've met that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.48,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes. Is that a problem somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.91,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.94,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,You mustn't speak of that girl to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.98,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Can you promise that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.20,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.60,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Umm, should I do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:03.87,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,That's plenty for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.19,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Could you come around the same time tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.08,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.70,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,This much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.55,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Please, don't be modest and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.45,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,You've done enough work to earn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.50,Default,Kurt,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.64,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,That isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.73,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I can't believe I allowed her to \Nmake contact with an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.64,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Even if I am doing this to slow \Nthe progression of the curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.02,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I've grown narrow sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.19,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I need to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:36.35,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,You can't be opening the curtains like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:40.02,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,It would be bad news if anyone \Nwere to see you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.16,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.22,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,My, your clothes are slightly loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.03,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,You have to wear them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:50.33,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.49,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I'm not used to putting them on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.09,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:57.09,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,You've always had someone taking care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.51,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Yes, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.19,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.23,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,It's been smelling so good for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.46,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Wait just a moment while I taste for poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.66,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.32,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,That man made it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.78,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,That man? You only met him briefly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.69,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,My intuition could tell he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:26.25,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Besides, my body's already in \Ntatters from the curse, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.27,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,There's no need to use poison \Nto kill me at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:32.71,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Please, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:36.68,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I have no idea who cast this curse on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:39.56,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,so I've had to suspect \Neveryone as I lived my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:44.26,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,But today at least, I'd like \Nto trust somebody all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.31,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.22,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Take your time eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:52.98,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,It smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.11,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,It must have some herbs in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.36,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,It tastes very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.28,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,It's heartwarming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:06.41,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Is it? I'm glad to hear that. Well, then I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.60,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Lise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:16.39,DefaultItalics,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Oh no! It was poisoned after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.45,DefaultItalics,Ophelia,0,0,0,,How could I be so careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.51,DefaultItalics,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.10,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I-I'll get you an antidote at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.89,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.32,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:32.74,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,You're fine?! Lise, look at \Nhow much you're sweating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.06,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I'm cured!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:34.96,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Cured?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.03,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Teacher, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:41.94,DefaultItalics,Ophelia,0,0,0,,The curse is fading?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.56,DefaultItalics,Ophelia,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.45,DefaultItalics,Ophelia,0,0,0,,She's healing too fast for a broken curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:49.85,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,This can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.65,Default,Curser,0,0,0,,My apologizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.51,Default,Curser,0,0,0,,I never expected the curse to be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.55,Default,Curser,0,0,0,,I'll recast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.95,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,They will not wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:58.50,Default,Curser,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.44,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,They have decided to resort to other means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:06.64,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,Lady Liselotte needs to die post haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.89,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Is Mimico in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.78,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Ophelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.35,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.52,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I came to discuss something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:22.11,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Yulishia might be an idiot, but \Nyou can definitely trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.04,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,If this is about some incident, \Nyou can get her involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.98,DefaultTop,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't go deciding that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.45,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Yulishia? The former adventurer working \Ndirectly under the royal family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:32.44,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I am the Atelier Meister, \NOphelia. And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:42.59,DefaultItalics,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Why?! Why, why, why is the third princess, \NLady Liselotte, in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:46.72,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Your Highness, I heard that you had fallen ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.86,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mimico.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.90,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,She wasn't actually sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.27,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,She was placed under a powerful curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.64,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,A curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:55.73,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.19,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Someone tried to assassinate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.02,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:04.09,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Lady Liselotte is the only child \Nborn between His Royal Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:09.66,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,and Princess Françoise, the woman he married \Nfrom the Gurumaku Empire to our East.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.83,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Her very existence is a symbol \Nof peace between our two nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:18.23,Default,Yulishia,0,0,0,,Meaning someone's trying to destroy \Nthose peaceful relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:19.19,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.83,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,With our war against the \Nnation to the north now over,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:25.80,Default,Ophelia,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are those who would \Nlike to spark a new conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:27.88,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.65,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.28,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Yes. Mimico...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:37.39,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,You came to me to identify \Nwho cast the curse, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:40.06,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,I was hoping we could rely on your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.76,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,My loyalty lies with His Royal Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.94,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,and her now departed Highness, Françoise,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.11,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,so I offer it to you, their daughter, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:53.79,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,However, Your Highness, it was \Na powerful curse, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.83,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you were able to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:56.94,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:22:00.85,Default,Lise,0,0,0,,That's all thanks to a man \Nwho called himself Kurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:02.41,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:03.80,Default,Mimico,0,0,0,,Ku—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:09.43,Default,Both,0,0,0,,K-Kurt?!
